(68, 'kml_68', 'hawkercentres', 103.843166992138, 1.27661461066321, '6', 'Existing', '13/12/2018', '', '', '52', '', 'Central', '', '108', '', '15/12/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/blk-6-tanjong-pagar-plaza.jpg', 'HUP Standard Upgrading', 'Tanjong Pagar Plaza Blk 6 (Blk 6 Tanjong Pagar Plaza Market and Food Centre)', 'I', 'Completed', '', '27/12/2013', 'Tanjong Pagar Plaza', '81006', 'Located near the Tanjong Pagar Plaza, the hawker centre serves some of the locals\' favourite dishes such as Hainanese Chicken Rice, Curry Fish Head and Seafood Soup. Built in 1977, the centre has 52 cooked food stalls and 108 market stalls to serve the needs of the patrons.', '', 'Blk 6, Tanjong Pagar Plaza, Singapore 081006'),
(69, 'kml_69', 'hawkercentres', 103.742891623681, 1.32084835041654, '37A', 'Existing', '26/11/2018', '', '', '28', '', 'West', '', '52', '', '30/11/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/resize_1262153022672.jpg', 'HUP Rebuilding', 'Teban Garden Road Blk 37A (Teban Gardens Market and Food Centre)', 'I', 'Completed', '', '3/1/2008', 'Teban Gardens Road', '601037', 'Located near Pandan Reservoir, the hawker centre comprises 28 cooked food stalls and 52 market stalls.  Built in 1976 to serve residents staying nearby.', '', 'Blk 37A, Teban Garden Road, Singapore 601037'),
(70, 'kml_70', 'hawkercentres', 103.807626838954, 1.27336828250285, '79', 'Existing', '12/11/2018', '', '', '40', '', 'West', '', '0', '', '13/11/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/resize_1262153497855.jpg', 'HUP Standard Upgrading', 'Telok Blangah Drive Blk 79 (Telok Blangah Food Centre)', 'I', 'Completed', '', '20/8/2005', 'Telok Blangah Drive', '100079', 'Situated directly opposite the Telok Blangah Community Centre, the hawker centre is a convenient location where residents of Telok Blangah can get to enjoy palatable local cuisines at affordable rates from the 40 cooked food stalls.', '', 'Blk 79, Telok Blangah Drive, Singapore 100079'),
(71, 'kml_71', 'hawkercentres', 103.775995008012, 1.33937596351523, '51', 'Existing', '3/12/2018', '', '', '84', '', 'West', '', '95', '', '3/12/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/resize_1265176195262.jpg', 'HUP Standard Upgrading', 'Bukit Timah Market', 'I', 'Completed', '', '2/1/2003', 'Upper Bukit Timah Road', '588215', 'Located along Upper Bukit Timah Road, the two-storey hawker centre was built in 1975 and was upgraded in 2003. A popular hawker centre serving the dining and marketing needs of residents living around Toh Yi Drive. Well-known for the variety of hawker fare, the centre is usually packed with patrons during peak hours. Comprises 84 cooked food stalls and 94 market stalls.', '', '51, Upper Bukit Timah Road, Singapore 588215'),
(72, 'kml_72', 'hawkercentres', 103.872090241567, 1.3397961360031, '202C', 'Under Construction', '#N/A', '', '', '0', '', '', 'hawker centre/flats/bus interchange', '0', '30/6/2017', '#N/A', '', 'New Centre', 'Woodleigh Village Hawker Centre', '', '#N/A', 'Woodleigh Village', '2021', 'Woodleigh Link', '363202', '', '21/7/2017', ''),
(73, 'kml_73', 'hawkercentres', 103.866536130299, 1.36422852315868, '20', 'Existing', '17/12/2018', '', '', '36', '', 'North', '', '0', '', '17/12/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/resize_1262155330191.jpg', 'HUP Standard Upgrading', 'Chomp Chomp Food Centre', 'I', 'Completed', '', '31/3/2004', 'Kensington Park Road', '557269', 'Located in Serangoon Gardens, Chomp Chomp Food Centre is well-known for its vibrant dinner and supper scene. Bustling with diners even till late at night, the 36 cooked food stalls in the small hawker centre serve popular local dishes such as Char Kway Teow, BBQ Chicken Wings, Seafood etc. This Centre attracts food lovers from all over the island.', '', '20, Kensington Park Road, Singapore 557269'),
(74, 'kml_74', 'hawkercentres', 103.882977999397, 1.37542896666561, '51', 'Existing (new)', '3/12/2018', '', '', '40', '', 'North', 'hawker centre/community club/family medicine clinic/senior care centre', '0', '', '3/12/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/ci-yuan-hawker-centre.jpg', 'New Centre', 'Ci Yuan Hawker Centre', '', '', '', '2015', 'Hougang Avenue 9', '538776', 'Built in 2015, Ci Yuan hawker centre is the first to be built since 1985. The hawker centre is located at the 1st storey of Ci Yuan Community Club and comprises of 40 cooked food stalls.  All the stalls are selling different food items and serving at least two items priced at $2.80 or below to ensure food price affordability. Ci Yuan hawker centre also has new facilities to accommodate the needs of different users to create a more pleasant dining experience for all.  These include family-friendly facilities such as child-friendly seating, point-of-sale system and self-payment kiosks.  For more information, please refer to: http://ciyuanhawker.com.sg/', '', '51 Hougang Avenue 9, Singapore 538776'),
(75, 'kml_75', 'hawkercentres', 103.885449224256, 1.32344525333847, '89', 'Existing', '10/12/2018', '', '', '41', '', 'East', '', '92', '', '10/12/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/resize_1262154127554.jpg', 'HUP Standard Upgrading', 'Circuit Road Blk 89', 'I', 'Completed', '', '8/4/2009', 'Circuit Road', '370089', 'Built in 1967, the hawker centre at Blk 89 Circuit Road comprises 40 cooked food stalls and 93 market stalls. One of the three hawker centres serving the residents living in the vicinity of Circuit Road.', '', 'Blk 89, Circuit Road, Singapore 370089'),
(76, 'kml_76', 'hawkercentres', 103.764264410293, 1.3037819726711, '726', 'Existing', '10/12/2018', '', '', '60', '', 'West', '', '135', '', '11/12/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/resize_1262155262246.jpg', 'HUP Standard Upgrading', 'Clementi West Street 2 Blk 726', 'I', 'Completed', '', '26/11/2009', 'Clementi West Street 2', '120726', 'Built in 1980, the hawker centre at Blk 726 Clementi West Street 2 consists of 60 cooked food stalls and 135 market stalls. The centre is conveniently located in close proximity to schools, housing estates and shopping complex.', '', 'Blk 726, Clementi West Street 2, Singapore 120726'),
(77, 'kml_77', 'hawkercentres', 103.870004415152, 1.32146226027018, '69', 'Existing', '10/12/2018', '', '', '84', '', 'East', '', '127', '', '12/12/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/blk-69-geylang-bahru.jpg', 'Opted out of HUP', 'Geylang Bahru Blk 69 (Blk 69 Geylang Bahru Market and Food Centre)', 'I', 'Completed', '', '', 'Geylang Bahru', '330069', 'Located near amenities such as swimming pool, industrial parks, commercial shops and residential estates, Blk 69 Geylang Bahru is a focal point where patrons get to enjoy local hawker fare at affordable prices. The hawker centre was built in 1974 and houses 84 cooked food stalls cum 127 market stalls.', '', 'Blk 69, Geylang Bahru, Singapore 330069'),
(78, 'kml_78', 'hawkercentres', 103.829626834637, 1.28797543998733, '22A/B', 'Existing', '17/12/2018', '', '', '30', '', 'Central', '', '0', '', '17/12/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/resize_1262152823428.jpg', 'HUP Standard Upgrading', 'Havelock Road Blk 22A/B (Havelock Road Cooked Food Centre)', 'I', 'Completed', '', '27/4/2007', 'Havelock Road', '161022', 'Built in 1969, the standalone hawker centre located in the Havelock area comprises 30 cooked food stalls. It was upgraded in 2007.', '', 'Blk 22A/B, Havelock Road, Singapore 161022/162022'),
(79, 'kml_79', 'hawkercentres', 103.822399230842, 1.44921660555282, '', 'Under Construction', '', '', '', '0', '', '', 'hawker centre/Town Sports and Recreational Centre/Primary Care Centre &amp; Senior Care Centre', '0', '1/5/2018', '', '', 'New Centre', 'Bukit Canberra Hawker Centre', '', '', '', '2020', '', '', '', '17/5/2018', ''),
(80, 'kml_80', 'hawkercentres', 103.814165010384, 1.32413422253318, '2', 'Existing', '10/12/2018', '', '', '32', '', 'Central', '', '0', '', '11/12/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/resize_1267437914368.jpg', 'HUP Standard Upgrading', 'Adam Road Food Centre', 'I', 'Completed', '', '30/4/2002', 'Adam Road', '289876', 'Built in 1974, Adam Food Centre comprises 32 cooked food stalls.  Although small in size, the hawker centre has a huge reputation.  Popular food offered in the centre includes BBQ Seafood, Nasi Lemak, Prawn Noodles etc.', '', '2, Adam Road, Singapore 289876'),
(81, 'kml_81', 'hawkercentres', 103.712799765872, 1.3452231627967, '221A/B', 'Existing', '17/12/2018', '', '', '72', '', 'West', '', '94', '', '18/12/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/resize_1262154766447.jpg', 'HUP Reconfiguration', 'Boon Lay Place Blk 221A/B (Boon Lay Place Market and Food Village)', 'I', 'Completed', '', '1/8/2004', 'Boon Lay Place', '641221', 'Located beside Boon Lay Shopping Centre, the hawker centre at Blk 221A/B Boon Lay Place provides marketing and dining amenities for residents living in Boon Lay. Built in 1976, the centre comprises 72 cooked food stalls and 94 market stalls.', '', 'Blk 221A/B, Boon Lay Place, Singapore 641221/642221'),
(82, 'kml_82', 'hawkercentres', 103.804489277779, 1.28629777221659, '120', 'Existing', '10/12/2018', '', '', '88', '', 'West', '', '0', '', '10/12/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/resize_1267852344747.jpg', 'HUP Standard Upgrading', 'Bukit Merah Lane 1 Blk 120 (Alexandra Village Food Centre)', 'I', 'Completed', '', '15/11/2010', 'Bukit Merah Lane 1', '150120', 'Opposite the Queenstown Shopping Centre, the hawker centre, also commonly known as Alexandra Food Village, is home to a number of yummylicious local dishes such as Chicken Rice, Claypot Laksa, Bak Ku Teh etc.', '', 'Blk 120, Bukit Merah Lane, Singapore 150120'),
(83, 'kml_83', 'hawkercentres', 103.904260878989, 1.32033178221424, '4A', 'Existing', '17/12/2018', '', '', '42', '', 'East', '', '71', '', '19/12/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/resize_1267873497497.jpg', 'HUP Standard Upgrading', 'Eunos Crescent Blk 4A', 'I', 'Completed', '', '30/3/2012', 'Eunos Crescent', '402004', 'The hawker centre at Blk 4A Eunos Crescent is located within close proximity to the Eunos MRT station and bus interchange. Its strategic location coupled with a wide variety of food offerings results in high patronage especially during lunch and dinner hours.', '', 'Blk 4A, Eunos Crescent, Singapore 402004'),
(84, 'kml_84', 'hawkercentres', 103.802903901116, 1.29323622090657, '159', 'Existing', '3/12/2018', '', '', '47', '', 'West', '', '66', '', '5/12/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/resize_1262154581891.jpg', 'HUP Reconfiguration', 'Mei Chin Road Blk 159 (Mei Chin Road Market)', 'I', 'Completed', '', '8/5/2009', 'Mei Chin Road', '140159', 'Built in 1970 to serve the Mei Ling estate, the hawker centre at Blk 159 Mei Chin Road was upgraded in 2009 to improve circulation space and ventilation. Comprises 47 cooked food stalls and 66 market stalls.', '', 'Blk 159, Mei Chin Road, Singapore 140159'),
(85, 'kml_85', 'hawkercentres', 103.794862936127, 1.31090802808558, '1', 'Existing', '17/12/2018', '', '', '21', '', 'West', '', '48', '', '17/12/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/resize_1267415509849.jpg', 'HUP Rebuilding', 'Holland Village Market and Food Centre', 'I', 'Completed', '', '12/12/2005', 'Lorong Mambong', '277700', 'Situated right in the heart of Holland Village, the hawker centre was built in the pre-war years. One of the hawker centres with the longest history in Singapore! Surrounded by restaurants and bistros, the hawker centre remains a popular choice for patrons with its offering of affordable hawker fare. Comprises 21 cooked food stalls and 48 market stalls.', '', '1, Lorong Mambong, Singapore 277700'),
(86, 'kml_86', 'hawkercentres', 103.890081064953, 1.35383739101169, '105', 'Existing', '17/12/2018', '', '', '51', '', 'North', '', '120', '', '18/12/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/resize_1259901634108.jpg', 'HUP Rebuilding', 'Hougang Ave 1 Blk 105 (Hougang 105 Hainanese Village Centre)', 'I', 'Completed', '', '11/11/2005', 'Hougang Ave 1', '530105', 'Also known as Hougang 105 Hainanese Village Centre, the hawker centre underwent a major facelift in 2005. A very popular hawker centre in the Hougang area, especially during the weekends. Serving the needs of both the residents of Lorong Ah Soo as well as the industrial area across at Defu Lane, there are currently 51 cooked food stalls and 120 market stalls within the centre.', '', 'Blk 105, Hougang Ave 1, Singapore 530105'),
(87, 'kml_87', 'hawkercentres', 103.808127999318, 1.28695275198944, '6', 'Existing', '17/12/2018', '', '', '96', '', 'Central', '', '48', '', '18/12/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/resize_1267760203.jpg', 'HUP Reconfiguration', 'Jalan Bukit Merah Blk 6 (ABC Brickworks Market/Food Centre)', 'I', 'Completed', '', '11/8/2006', 'Jalan Bukit Merah', '150006', 'Fondly known as ABC Brickworks Market, it is within close proximity to Alexandra Food Village and IKEA. The hawker centre, which was built in 1974, is another alternative for the residents of Queenstown and Bukit Merah.  Patrons can find delicious yet affordable hawker fare at the centre.', '', 'Blk 6, Jalan Bukit Merah, Singapore 150006'),
(88, 'kml_88', 'hawkercentres', 103.839945947186, 1.28823055540002, '1', 'Existing', '17/12/2018', '', '', '21', '', 'Central', '', '0', '', '17/12/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/resize_1267874440744.jpg', 'HUP Standard Upgrading', 'Jalan Kukoh Blk 1 (Kukoh 21 Food Centre)', 'I', 'Completed', '', '4/10/2010', 'Jalan Kukoh', '161001', 'Built in 1969, Blk 1 Jalan Kukoh used to consist of both a market and food section. After upgrading in 2010, the centre was converted to a food centre with 21 cooked food stalls.', '', 'Blk 1, Jalan Kukoh, Singapore 161001'),
(89, 'kml_89', 'hawkercentres', 103.731579747132, 1.34531247026793, '347', 'Existing', '17/12/2018', '', '', '56', '', 'West', '', '169', '', '18/12/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/resize_1275537901886.jpg', 'HUP Standard Upgrading', 'Jurong East Ave 1 Blk 347 (Yuhua Market and Hawker Centre)', 'I', 'Completed', '', '31/12/2002', 'Jurong East Ave 1', '600347', 'Located near to the PIE exit (Jurong Town Hall Road), the hawker centre at Blk 347 Jurong East Ave 1 is popular with residents living in the area. A wide variety of food and market produce is offered at the hawker centre by the 56 cooked food stalls and 169 market stalls. It was built in 1984 to cater to the dining and marketing needs of residents.', '', 'Blk 347, Jurong East Ave 1, Singapore 600347'),
(90, 'kml_90', 'hawkercentres', 103.737781231485, 1.34344213770991, '254', 'Existing', '10/12/2018', '', '', '60', '', 'West', '', '87', '', '11/12/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/resize_1265167615307.jpg', 'HUP Reconfiguration', 'Jurong East Street 24 Blk 254 (Yuhua Village Market and Food Centre)', 'I', 'Completed', '', '5/7/2006', 'Jurong East Street 24', '600254', 'Located near to the PIE exit (Jurong Town Hall Road), the hawker centre at Blk 254 Jurong East Street 24 serves the marketing and dining needs of residents living in Yuhua Village.  There are 60 cooked food stalls and 87 market produce stalls operating within the hawker centre. Originally built in 1983.', '', 'Blk 254, Jurong East Street 24, Singapore 600254'),
(91, 'kml_91', 'hawkercentres', 103.846606784092, 1.27921844263268, '', 'Existing', '12/1/2019', '', '', '134', '', 'Central', '', '1', '', '13/1/2019', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/resize_1265968760190.jpg', 'HUP Standard Upgrading', 'Amoy Street Food Centre (Telok Ayer Food Centre)', 'I', 'Completed', 'National Development Building', '17/2/2003', 'Telok Ayer Street', '69111', 'Built in 1983, the two-storey food centre is located within the central business district.  Housing many well-known stalls, the centre has evolved into a favourite lunch venue for executives working near Shenton Way. Be spoilt by the choice of hawker fare at affordable prices!', '', 'National Development Building, Annex B, Telok Ayer Street, Singapore 069111'),
(92, 'kml_92', 'hawkercentres', 103.856853966617, 1.30733651651517, '166', 'Existing', '3/12/2018', '', '', '66', '', 'Central', '', '0', '', '4/12/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/resize_1265176120532.jpg', 'HUP Standard Upgrading', 'Berseh Food Centre', 'I', 'Completed', '', '5/3/2004', 'Jalan Besar', '208877', 'Located along Jalan Besar Road, Berseh Food Centre houses 66 cooked food stalls. Built in 1975, the food centre presents an added nostalgic flavour with the rows of meticulously restored pre-war shophouses surrounding it.', '', '166, Jalan Besar, Singapore 208877'),
(93, 'kml_93', 'hawkercentres', 103.850530969624, 1.30620584090733, '665', 'Existing', '3/12/2018', '', '', '119', '', 'Central', '', '284', '', '4/12/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/resize_1262156313186.jpg', 'HUP Standard Upgrading', 'Buffalo Road Blk 665 (Tekka Centre/Zhu Jiao Market)', 'I', 'Completed', '', '30/6/2009', 'Buffalo Road', '210665', 'More commonly known as Tekka Centre, the hawker centre is a popular haunt for marketing and dining needs, especially with the Indian community. An amazing variety of fresh produce is sold at the market.  Built in 1980, it is the second largest hawker centre in Singapore housing more than 400 stalls. An iconic landmark in the Little India area!', '', 'Blk 665, Buffalo Road, Singapore 210665'),
(94, 'kml_94', 'hawkercentres', 103.895609494855, 1.3151420505272, '13/14', 'Existing', '3/12/2018', '', '', '72', '', 'East', '', '146', '', '6/12/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/resize_1267848993155.jpg', 'HUP Reconfiguration', 'Haig Road Blk 13/14 (Haig Road Market and Cooked Food Centre)', 'I', 'Completed', '', '4/8/2010', 'Haig Road', '430013', 'Built in 1977, the hawker centre at Blk 13/14 Haig Road is easily visible from Changi Road. Comprising 72 cooked food stalls and 146 market stalls, its ideal location as well as the wide selection of affordable hawker fare have attracted many residents and working professionals around the vicinity.', '', 'Blk 13/14, Haig Road, Singapore 430013/430014'),
(95, 'kml_95', 'hawkercentres', 103.772489583206, 1.37760053528611, '2', 'Existing (new)', '3/12/2018', '', '', '28', '', 'West', '', '45', '', '4/12/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/bukit-panjang-hawker-centre.jpg', 'New Centre', 'Bukit Panjang Hawker Centre', '', '', '', '2015', 'Bukit Panjang Ring Road', '679947', 'Bukit Panjang Hawker Centre &amp; Market is one of the 10 new centres announced by the Government. Among the 10 centres, it is the second to start operations, after the Hougang Ci Yuan Hawker Centre. Bukit Panjang Hawker Centre &amp; Market has 28 cooked food stalls, 14 market slab stalls and 14 lock-up stalls located on both floors of the two-storeyed building.  It also has a sundry store on the second floor.', '', '2 Bukit Panjang Ring Road, Singapore 679947'),
(96, 'kml_96', 'hawkercentres', 103.854482811591, 1.37276992816898, '527', 'Existing', '10/12/2018', '', '', '50', '', 'North', '', '100', '', '17/12/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/resize_1265165592824.jpg', 'HUP Reconfiguration', 'Ang Mo Kio Ave 10 Blk 527 (Cheng San Market and Cooked Food Centre)', 'I', 'Completed', '', '21/2/2004', 'Ang Mo Kio Ave 10', '560527', 'Commonly known as Cheng San Market and Cooked Food Centre, Blk 527 Ang Mo Kio Ave 10 is one of the three hawker centres located along Ang Mo Kio Ave 10. The hawker centre was built in 1979 to serve the dining and marketing needs of nearby residents. Upgraded in 2004, it houses 50 cooked food stalls and 100 market stalls.', '', 'Blk 527, Ang Mo Kio Ave 10, Singapore 560527'),
(97, 'kml_97', 'hawkercentres', 103.779784899996, 1.43353885680037, '4', 'Existing (new)', '19/11/2018', '', '', '70', '', 'North', 'hawker centre/supermarket/shops', '0', '4/9/2015', '21/11/2018', 'http://www.nea.gov.sg/images/default-source/Hawker-Centres-Division/mmhc.jpg', 'New Replacement Centre', 'Marsiling Mall Hawker Centre', '', '', 'Marsiling Mall', '2017', 'Woodlands Street 12', '738623', 'Built in 2017, and located close to the heart of Woodlands, Marsiling Mall Hawker Centre offers residents convenient access to a variety of good and affordable hawker food. This hawker centre is also situated adjacent to Woodlands Sports Centre, bringing hawker food to the doorstep of sports facility users.', '1/1/2016', 'Blk 4,Woodlands St 12,Singapore 738623'),
