(34, 'kml_34', 'monuments', 103.847853439392, 1.29933187185483, '2', '', '229233', 'Handy Road', '', 'https://roots.sg/Roots/Content/Places/national-monuments/former-cathay-building-now-the-cathay', 'Former Cathay Building (now The Cathay)', 'https://roots.sg/~/media/Roots/Images/monuments/022-former-cathay-building/former-cathay-building-01.png', '', '', 'The Art Deco façade wall fronting the modern glass architecture of The Cathay is the remnant of what used to be Malaya’s tallest building.'),
